snippet.title: Nobody's Left | 12 Minutes Exclusive Gameplay.
snippet.description:
Hey Guys! we are excited to share with you our first ever recording on nobody's left Demo. here you will get to see some of the actions, interactions and environments for the first time! As exciting as it is for all of us, we would also want to make sure we can later distinct the early supporters when we grow. so please use the link in the bio to put in your name as an early supporter and secure your bonuses for FREE!

Sit back, relax and enjoy.
